# Netlify Redirects Configuration for Rosehill Rail
# Redirects from rosehillrail.com to rail.rosehill.group

# Force old domain to new subdomain
https://rosehillrail.com/* https://rail.rosehill.group/:splat 301!
http://rosehillrail.com/* https://rail.rosehill.group/:splat 301!
https://www.rosehillrail.com/* https://rail.rosehill.group/:splat 301!
http://www.rosehillrail.com/* https://rail.rosehill.group/:splat 301!

# Force HTTPS
http://rail.rosehill.group/* https://rail.rosehill.group/:splat 301!
http://rosehillrail.netlify.app/* https://rosehillrail.netlify.app/:splat 301!

